Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.selenium.api.widget

Annotation Type Label

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target({METHOD,FIELD})
public @interface Label
    It is possible to find some web element by the full text matching. Labels (titles, texts of related elements, visible values of some attributes etc) is alternative way to find some element/group of elements described by Widget.

    This annotation should mark methods of a Widget that return String and have no parameters. Values which are returned by these methods play role of labels.

    Also this annotation may mark WebElement fields. Text content (WebElement.getText()) of these elements are considered labels.
